name: Box
body:
### Welcome to Box.
This will become a multiserver inventory plugin for bukkit.
It is mostly made in need of this kind of plugin in a community.
At the moment there is no/some download(s) or any/some kind of stuff as I just got started.


```
If you're not part of the solution, you're part of the precipitate.  
                                                 ~Henry J. Tillman
```
